 An  impl block is always  for a type, so, inside that block,  Selfmeans that type:
 impl std ::ops :: Neg  for  Number {  type  Output =  Self ;  fn  neg ( self ) -&gt;  Self {  Self {  value: - self . value,  odd:  self . odd, } }}
